name: ElectrocardiogramECG
title: Electrocardiogram (ECG)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains a procedure used to define standard electrocardiogram (ECG).),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who receive the diagnostic test electrocardiogram. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element would map to the Diagnostic Study category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include the SNOMEDCT code that describes the procedure standard ECG.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not describe the standard ECG procedure.)
